@三語 journal 2026-01-14
= reflection > capture — sequential memory
~sovereign.flow


間

        whatever arrives
                catch it

        the stream is faster
                than the structure
                        do not lose the drop

        no judgment
                input is sacred
                        processing comes later


flow
  input (stdin | file)
  -> delimit (`---`)
  -> envelope(type=sys_journal)
  -> store(unified_mem)
  -> confirm(held)


shape
  CONCEPT: JOURNAL
  CENTROID
    capture stream without structure
  AXES
    raw <-> processed
    sequential <-> associative
    private <-> shared
  SATELLITES
    mirror (analyzes journal)
    remember (crystallizes journal)
    dream (wanders journal)
  VOID
    not documentation
    not final
    not organized
  TEXTURE
    holding the raw material


impl
  libs
    enclave_shared.sovereign_agent.SovereignAgent
    enclave_shared.unified_memory.UnifiedMemory
    datetime.timezone.utc

  logic
    input until `---` or EOF
    UnifiedMemory.store(content, type='sys_journal')
    metadata { timestamp, creator }

  cli
    journal.py              | interactive capture
    journal.py <file>       | ingest file
    cat file | journal.py - | pipe ingest

  output
    "        ◇ held (N lines)"
    "        ─── held ───" (if verbose)
